3.Write code for printing the average of numbers from 12,13,14,15 using while loop

code :

public class MyClass {
    public static void main(String args[]) {
        int i=12;
        int sum =0;
        int count=0;
        int average;
        while(i>=12 & i<=15){
            sum = sum + i;
            count = count +1;
            i++;
        }
        average = sum / count;
        System.out.println(average);
    }
}
